name: blessings
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "blessings" %}
{% set version = "1.7" %}
{% set sha256 = "98e5854d805f50a5b58ac2333411b0482516a8210f23f43308baeb58d77c157d" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 1006
  skip: True  # [win]
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - blessings

about:
  home: https://github.com/erikrose/blessings
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A thin, practical wrapper around terminal capabilities in Python '
  dev_url: https://github.com/erikrose/blessings

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - synapticarbors
